# CHANAKYA Radar

- AI Deal Health Board — **not** a workflow or lender-stage board.
- Kanban **only** — no List / Table / Calendar; cards **never** draggable.
- Columns fixed: On Track · Needs Attention · At Risk · Dormant · On Hold · Completed.
- Card click opens the **Active Workspace** (Strategic Bench / Credit Bench / Loan Workspace) — CHANAKYA decides.
- Cards answer in ≤5s: what deal, why concern, who blocking, what next, where to work, expected outcome.
- Show: Next Workspace, Waiting On, Last Activity, Active lenders (max 3), CHANAKYA Says, Why?, Recommends (max 3), Expected Outcome, Momentum, Priority, Ageing; Confidence at bottom.
- Never show Rejected / Lost / Cancelled / Withdrawn / Closed lenders.
